title: Qatar Real Estate Price Index
description: Housing Index in Qatar increased to 213.69 points in September from 209.05 points in August of 2022. Housing Index in Qatar averaged 246.03 points from 2015 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 311 points in November of 2015 and a record low of 202.30 points in February of 2021. Real Estate Price Index in Qatar is designed to measure the change in the average level of prices paid for real estate properties sold in the country. This page provides - Qatar Housing Index- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Qatar Central Bank
